define Taylor = Character("Taylor")
define Hayden = Character("Hayden")
define Logan = Character("Logan")
define Bella = Character("Bella")
define Alex = Character("Alex")
define Julie = Character("Julie")
define Kyle = Character("Kyle")

label scene16:

    # Show a background. This uses a placeholder by default, but you can
    # add a file (named either "bg room.png" or "bg room.jpg") to the
    # images directory to show it.

    scene bg room

    image Taylor = "TaylorPlaceholder.png"
    image Hayden = "HaydenPlaceholder.png"
    image Logan = "LoganPlaceholder.png"
    image Bella = "BellaPlaceholder.png"
    image Alex = "AlexPlaceholder.png"
    image Julie = "JuliePlaceholder.png"
    image Kyle = "KylePlaceholder.png"

    show Taylor at left:
        zoom 0.65
    show Logan at right

    Taylor "Regardless. There’s still people that need to be freed. If I must free them alone, I will. But-"

    hide Logan
    show Bella at right

    Bella "WHAT?! I am NOT letting you go alone!"

    hide Taylor
    show Hayden at left:
        zoom 0.75

    Hayden "Come on Sis! We aren’t doing anything by ourselves anymore! We got a team!"

    hide Bella
    show Alex at right

    Alex "…I mean…I guess I could come along. But that’s it!"

    hide Hayden
    show Logan at left

    Logan "Shit, I could go for another spin. Let’s go pop this popsicle joint!"

    hide Alex
    show Julie at right

    Julie "Go save the day again! You guys are so AWESOME! Like AWESOME AWESOMEEEE! And then…WE CAN GET TACOSSSS! Or even better…DONUTS!"

    hide Logan
    show Kyle at left

    Kyle "YES! I WANT MORE DONUTS! THE DONUT VENDOR ISN’T HERE!"

    show Taylor at center

    Taylor "You got it, Juls!"

    hide Kyle
    hide Julie

    Taylor "So we left again and went towards the labor camps, the prisons, and the execution holdings. We shared the good news, freeing everyone in the process, and let them walk off into the sun once again. Freeing them from the lives they’ve lived."

    Taylor "Freedom was an odd feeling, but…we saved everyone from being killed. From being tortured after all these years. But now I have a team…I have…friends. Most importantly, I have my brother."

    Taylor "We came together and took down a mighty foe. And we did so…with our strength."

    scene black with fade

    "THE END"